name: ATXDillo
0:
”Alexa, ask Dillo to dig me up a happy hour.”
”Alexa, ask Dillo to dig me up a happy hour on Sunday.”
”Alexa, ask Dillo to get me a show.”
skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dillo
des: Looking for something random to do in Austin? Have an Echo? Well now is your chance to ask for a random happy hour or event around town, simply by asking Dillo to dig it up. You can either ask for a random happy hour or event happening tonight, or ask according to day of the week Monday through Sunday. UPDATED with images for the Amazon Echo Show!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
